items.title: WSAStartup not yet performed [WSANOTINITIALISED ]
items.body:
Everysingle time i open up my wallet, and view my TOR log file.. this is the first line in the log file:

**Apr 09 15:55:43.000 [err] libevent call with win32 failed: Successful WSAStartup not yet performed [WSANOTINITIALISED ] [10093]**

From my understanding this is part of the microsoft MSDN aspx library.

Has anybody else had this issue and know how to solve it? I cannot figure out an easy fix on my own.

Not sure if this is what causes my tor log file to look like this after conneting, it constantly scrubs connections and never seems to really find a good connection to TOR. Is the WSAStartup part of the issue possibly?
